metadata.name: Crystal Frogs Gen 2 #1
metadata.description: Crystal Frog #1 is an integral part of the Gen 2 Crystal Frogs collection, an ever-expanding community of passionate supporters who are driving the Crystal Frogs animated series forward. Stake your Gen 2 frog, earn crystals, and become a vital voice in the on-chain voting that shapes the narrative of our captivating cartoon episodes. Together, we are ushering in a new era of interactive storytelling and community empowerment. Ribbit!
